Discounts must be applied to qualifying orders that are of equal or lesser value. For 35% off, purchase a complete pair of sunglasses in addition to a second complete pair. Qualifying purchases include any prescription polarized or non-polarized sun lens & frame purchase. The least expensive pair(s) will receive the 35% discount.

seoItemMetaData.metaTitle: Meta Quest 2 - Virtual Reality Gaming System, All-In-One Wireless VR Headset, 256GB
seoItemMetaData.metaDescription: Experience ultimate immersion with the wireless Meta Quest 2 VR Headset. Explore limitless worlds with 256GB storage space.

product.shortDescription: Meta Quest 2 is the all-in-one system that truly sets you free to explore in VR. With no wires or cables, simply put on the headset, draw out your play space, and jump into fully-immersive, imagination-defying worlds. A fast processor and immersive graphics keeps your experience smooth and seamless, even as high-speed action unfolds around you. 3D positional audio, hand tracking and easy-to-use controllers make virtual worlds feel real. A built-in battery lets you explore further for longer as you discover a growing library of over 500 titles across gaming, social/multiplayer, fitness and entertainment. Incredible social spaces and multiplayer arenas let you meet, play and build communities with people from all over the world. Travel universes in blockbuster fantasies, scare yourself witless in horror adventures or collaborate with colleagues in innovative workspaces. Sit front row with friends and family at movies and live events, find your new workout crew or join quests with fellow adventurers. And you can connect your VR headset to a gaming-compatible computer (PC and cable sold separately). Let your friends and family into your VR world by casting your experience to compatible TVs and other screens. And anywhere you go in the real world, you can take your lightweight, portable Quest 2 with you. *Requires mobile device, wifi and companion app for setup. Account registration required. Meta Quest is for ages 13+. Certain apps, games and experiences may be suitable for a more mature audience.

groups.shortDescription:
Protect it today, enjoy it for years.

Get award-winning Allstate service and support that goes above and beyond the manufacturer’s warranty.

Gaming hardware plans cover:

  • Accidents like cracked screens & liquid damage
  • Mechanical & electrical failures like controller drift, broken buttons & speaker failure
  • Fast repairs & replacements with easy online claims available 24/7
  • Includes 100% parts & labor with no hidden fees

When you add your new gaming hardware to cart, be sure to add a Walmart Protection Plan, too.

Simply add your plan at checkout. There’s no need to register your plan for it to be active. We’ll email you protection plan details after you check out.

genAiDetails.genAiDescription: The Meta Quest 2 is an all-in-one wireless VR headset with  256GB of storage , offering a fully immersive experience with  3D positional audio , hand tracking, and easy-to-use controllers. It features a  fast processor  and  immersive graphics , allowing for smooth gameplay and exploration of over 500 titles across gaming, fitness, social/multiplayer, and entertainment. The headset is portable, with a built-in battery, and can be set up easily without a PC or console. It also includes safety features, such as designated play space alerts, and is suitable for ages 13+. With its  wireless design  and intuitive controls, the Meta Quest 2 provides a seamless and immersive VR experience.
genAiDetails.genAiDescriptionBullet:
• Total Immersion: Experience total immersion with 3D positional audio, hand tracking, and easy-to-use controllers making virtual worlds feel real.
  • Expansive Library: Explore over 500 titles across gaming, fitness, social/multiplayer, and entertainment, including exclusive releases and unique VR experiences.
  • Fast Performance: Enjoy fast, smooth gameplay and immersive graphics with a fast processor and high-speed action.
  • Wireless Freedom: Be truly free to explore in VR with a wireless headset, intuitive controls, built-in battery, and no PC or console needed.
  • Social Connectivity: Come together in social spaces and multiplayer arenas, attend live events, find workout crews, or join adventures with fellow players.
  • Portable Design: Take your lightweight, portable Quest 2 with you anywhere, with no extra equipment needed.
  • Safety Features: Play without worries by setting your designated play space and get alerts if you move outside it; see child safety guidance for age suitability.

reviewSummary.summary: The Meta Quest 2 is a highly praised product, offering an exceptional gaming experience with seamless performance, immersive gameplay, and a user-friendly interface. While opinions on battery life and value are mixed, customers agree it's a great gift, providing amazing fun and entertainment. Comfort is generally good, but some users experience issues. Overall, it's a great choice for those seeking a fun experience.
reviewSummary.summaryTitle: Exceptional gaming experience with seamless performance and immersive gameplay

customerReviews.reviewText: I love everything about this! I have never had so much fun playing video games in my life! And don’t get me started about the theater style movies I can watch in my fancy living room inside the oculus. I would live inside there forever if I could lol.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: I want to live virtual forever!!!!!!

customerReviews.reviewText: It works just like regular no issues after having it for months now there’s just not a lot of fun games to play they need to start making and adding more it’s just the same ones over and over again plus most creators don’t really update there games because it’s just set to one thing/storyline
I bought it for my son for Christmas, he was very excited he’s been asking for it for a while. I was upset it cost 499.99 and after I purchased it I kept seeing it online for cheaper.

All I can say is this is amazing, and I know I haven't even scratched the surface of what I can do!  Easy set up and lots of good sources available for questions, tips, maintenance etc.  And I got a better price through Walmart too!

Bought this for my dad and he LOVED it. He won't stop talking about it. I also gave it a shot and the picture was so realistic. I can see why he loves it so much. I was worried about him playing alone and hitting things but I love that you can set boundaries so when you step outside those boundaries you set you no longer see the game you see the area you're playing in with the headset on still.
Purchased for my son for his 10th birthday in June. Happy to say he is happy with it! No issues

received the oculus 2 256 GB, went to set it up after being charged on Christmas day, discovered it didn't work at all, the screen was black, wont do anything.  I received the run around from customer service, finally they said they'd contact seller. I ended up exchanging for a meta Quest 3s 256 GB since I could get what I paid for in the beginning. I also will have to contact Walmart Customer Care to get a refund on the warranty I paid in the beginning. 
Buy at store, advise, not to buy online from a marketplace seller through walmart.com, you probably will get the run around if the product is defective.

I ordered the 256GB one and received the 128GB. I contacted the seller and they only asked for a picture of the one they sent, i sent it, tried reaching out again and then they stopped responding to me. What a ripoff!

This device stopped working 3 months into having it and the customer service told me to do a hard reset because nothing else would work. Now it won't sync. This app you have to use to connect is buggy and leads to hours of frustration. I'm returning it.
Had to return item due to not working couldn't get it to turn on.. Kids didn't get to enjoy their gift sadly..
